statements: SELECT id, age, sex, genetic_variation, geographical_location FROM natural_selection_analysis;
SELECT sex, geographical_location, age, genetic_variation, id FROM natural_selection_analysis;
SELECT id, sex, geographical_location FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE age > 30;
SELECT age, sex FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE geographical_location = 'Africa';
SELECT id, age FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE genetic_variation < 0.05;
SELECT id, age, sex, genetic_variation, geographical_location FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY age DESC
SELECT id, sex, genetic_variation, geographical_location FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE geographical_location = 'Africa' ORDER BY sex ASC
SELECT id, age, sex, genetic_variation, geographical_location FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE sex = 'Male' ORDER BY genetic_variation DESC
SELECT id, sex, geographical_location FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE age < 50 ORDER BY geographical_location ASC
SELECT id, age, geographical_location FROM natural_selection_analysis WHERE genetic_variation > 0.5 ORDER BY age ASC
SELECT * FROM Population;
SELECT population_name, average_height FROM Population WHERE population_size > 1000;
SELECT population_name, population_size FROM Population ORDER BY population_size DESC;
SELECT * FROM StatisticalAnalysis WHERE analysis_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT analysis_id, population_name, analysis_result->>'average_income' AS average_income FROM StatisticalAnalysis JOIN Population ON StatisticalAnalysis.population_id = Population.population_id;
SELECT population_name, average_height FROM Population;
SELECT * FROM Population WHERE population_size > 1000;
SELECT analysis_id, analysis_result FROM StatisticalAnalysis WHERE analysis_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT * FROM StatisticalAnalysis JOIN Population ON StatisticalAnalysis.population_id = Population.population_id;
SELECT analysis_date, population_name, analysis_result FROM StatisticalAnalysis JOIN Population ON StatisticalAnalysis.population_id = Population.population_id WHERE analysis_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM population_data;
SELECT age, sex, trait FROM population_data WHERE sex = 'Male';
SELECT population_id, age, trait FROM population_data ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT population_id, COUNT(id) as total_count FROM population_data GROUP BY population_id;
SELECT * FROM statistical_analysis WHERE result > 0.5;
SELECT * FROM population_data WHERE age > 30 ORDER BY sex DESC, trait ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT trait, result FROM statistical_analysis WHERE result > 0.5 AND attribute = 'height' ORDER BY result DESC;
SELECT pattern_description FROM selection_patterns WHERE pattern_id IN (1, 3, 5, 7) AND population_id = 100 ORDER BY pattern_id ASC;
SELECT population_id, sex, COUNT(*) AS total_count FROM population_data GROUP BY population_id, sex HAVING total_count > 50 ORDER BY total_count DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT trait FROM population_data WHERE age BETWEEN 20 AND 40 ORDER BY trait ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM population;
SELECT species, age FROM population WHERE age > 10;
SELECT * FROM natural_selection_events ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT event_id, selection_pressure FROM natural_selection_events WHERE selection_pressure > 0.5;
SELECT analysis_id, sample_size, analysis_results FROM statistical_analysis;
SELECT * FROM population;
SELECT individual_id, species FROM population ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT * FROM natural_selection_events WHERE selection_pressure > 0.5;
SELECT event_id, event_date FROM natural_selection_events WHERE event_date < NOW() - INTERVAL '1 week';
SELECT population_id, mean_age, variance_age FROM population_statistics WHERE variance_age > 10;
SELECT id, population_size FROM Population;
SELECT phenotype, fitness FROM Individual ORDER BY fitness DESC;
SELECT allele, mutation_rate FROM GeneticVariation WHERE mutation_rate > 0.1;
SELECT * FROM SelectionPressure WHERE type = 'Tournament';
SELECT model_name, description FROM EvolutionaryModel WHERE id > 5;
SELECT * FROM Population WHERE generation_number > 100 ORDER BY average_fitness DESC;
SELECT phenotype, fitness FROM Individual WHERE fitness > 0.8 ORDER BY phenotype ASC, fitness DESC;
SELECT model_name, description FROM EvolutionaryModel WHERE model_name LIKE '%genetic%' ORDER BY model_name ASC;
SELECT allele, mutation_rate FROM GeneticVariation WHERE mutation_rate < 0.05 ORDER BY allele DESC;
SELECT population_id, type, intensity FROM SelectionPressure WHERE type = 'Natural Selection' ORDER BY intensity DESC;
